OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBoost sport to get pupils  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fback to school - report    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, More sport in school and investment in 
OL,6, youth clubs are needed to tackle the   
OL,7, number of children regularly missing   
OL,8, class, according to a new report.      
OL,10,FMore than one in five children in      
OL,11,FEngland are persistently absent from   
OL,12,Fschool.                                
OL,14,FThe Centre for Social Justice (CSJ)    
OL,15,Freport says some parents think children
OL,16,Fdo not need to be in school full-time. 
OL,18,FThe Department for Education (DfE) says
OL,19,Fparents have a duty to ensure their    
OL,20,Fchild goes to school.                  
